    <title>&lt;MM&gt;线性规划</title>
    <url>/2024/08/08/2024-08-03-%5BMM%5D%E7%BA%BF%E6%80%A7%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="示例及定义"><a href="#示例及定义" class="headerlink" title="示例及定义"></a>示例及定义</h2><p>例1.1 </p>
<blockquote>
<p>某机床厂生产甲、乙两种机床，每台销售后的利润分别为 4千元与 3 千元。生产甲机床需用A、B机器加工，加工时间分别为每台 2 小时和 1 小时；生产乙机床需用A、B、C三种机器加工，加工时间为每台各一小时。若每天可用于加工的机器时数分别为A机器 10 小时、B机器 8小时和C机器7小时，问该厂应生产甲、乙机床各几台，才能使总利润最大?</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic/202408081752275.png"></p>
<p>目标函数及约束条件均为线性函数，故被称为线性规划问题。线性规划问题是在一组线性约束条件的限制下，求一线性目标函数最大或最小的问题。</p>
<p>在解决实际问题时，把问题归结成一个线性规划数学模型是很重要的一步，往往也是很困难的一步，模型建立得是否恰当，直接影响到求解。而选适当的决策变量，是我们建立有效模型的关键之一。</p>
<h2 id="解的概念"><a href="#解的概念" class="headerlink" title="解的概念"></a>解的概念</h2><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818179.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818145.png"></p>
<h2 id="Matlab标准型"><a href="#Matlab标准型" class="headerlink" title="Matlab标准型"></a>Matlab标准型</h2><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818357.png"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>linprog只能求解最小值，如果求最大值须在目标函数之前添加 <code>-</code>(负号)  </p>
</blockquote>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818745.png"></p>
<h2 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h2><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818117.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818979.png"></p>
<h2 id="转化为线性规划的问题"><a href="#转化为线性规划的问题" class="headerlink" title="转化为线性规划的问题"></a>转化为线性规划的问题</h2><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818125.png"></p>
<h2 id="应用"><a href="#应用" class="headerlink" title="应用"></a>应用</h2><h3 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h3><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818841.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818514.png"></p>
<h3 id="符号规定及基本假设"><a href="#符号规定及基本假设" class="headerlink" title="符号规定及基本假设"></a>符号规定及基本假设</h3><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818590.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031818791.png"></p>
<h3 id="模型建立"><a href="#模型建立" class="headerlink" title="模型建立"></a>模型建立</h3><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819227.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819178.png"></p>
<h3 id="模型分析"><a href="#模型分析" class="headerlink" title="模型分析"></a>模型分析</h3><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819021.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819633.png"></p>
<h3 id="模型求解"><a href="#模型求解" class="headerlink" title="模型求解"></a>模型求解</h3><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819652.png"></p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Matlab"><figure class="iseeu highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">%linprog%</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">clc,clear</span><br><span class="line">a=<span class="number">0</span>;<span class="built_in">hold</span> on</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> a&lt;<span class="number">0.05</span></span><br><span class="line">    c=[<span class="number">-0.05</span>,<span class="number">-0.27</span>,<span class="number">-0.19</span>,<span class="number">-0.185</span>,<span class="number">-0.185</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    A=[<span class="built_in">zeros</span>(<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">1</span>),<span class="built_in">diag</span>([<span class="number">0.025</span>,<span class="number">0.015</span>,<span class="number">0.055</span>,<span class="number">0.026</span>])];</span><br><span class="line">    b=a*<span class="built_in">ones</span>(<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    Aeq=[<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">1.01</span>,<span class="number">1.02</span>,<span class="number">1.045</span>,<span class="number">1.065</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    beq=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    LB=<span class="built_in">zeros</span>(<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    [x,Q]=linprog(c,A,b,Aeq,beq,LB);</span><br><span class="line">    Q=-Q;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">plot</span>(a,Q,<span class="string">'*k'</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    a=a+<span class="number">0.001</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">end</span></span><br><span class="line">xlabel(<span class="string">'a'</span>),ylabel(<span class="string">'Q'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819831.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819653.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819664.png"></p>
<h2 id="练习"><a href="#练习" class="headerlink" title="练习"></a>练习</h2><p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819004.png"></p>
<p><img lazyload="" src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://pic-1328468418.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic%2F202408031819992.png"></p>
]]></content>
